Notes for https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=e9Ucb1JHUfQ

* Markup syntax
- *Bold*
- /italic/
- =verbatim= is for verbatim text without any special meaning. This is equivalent to ~\verb~
- ~code~ is for actual code. Think of this as an inline ~\begin{minted}~
- _underline_
  
